OL,3,CReform promises tax cuts so big even
OL,4,CLiz Truss might think them gung-ho
OL,6,FITV News Business Editor Joel Hills
OL,7,Fbreaks down the Reform manifesto and
OL,8,Fit's massive tax cuts
OL,10,FA combination of high debt interest
OL,11,Fcosts and low economic growth means
OL,12,Fwhoever forms the next government is
OL,13,Flikely to find money is very tight.
OL,15,FBut Reform's manifesto is definitely
OL,16,Fnot shy. It proposes tax cuts and
OL,17,Fspending increases worth #141 billion
OL,18,Fa year.
