OL,3,CReform promises tax cuts so big even
OL,4,CLiz Truss might think them gung-ho
OL,6,FThere's more money for defence (with a
OL,7,Fpledge to raise spending to 3% of
OL,8,Fnational income) and a lot more money
OL,9,Ffor health, along with a commitment to
OL,10,Feliminate the NHS waiting list
OL,11,Faltogether - something that has never
OL,12,Fhappened ever since the NHS was formed.
OL,14,FThe tax cuts are eye-catching. Reform
OL,15,Fsays it would take 7 million people
OL,16,Fout of paying income tax by raising
OL,17,Fthe threshold to #20,000 a year.
