OL,3,CReform promises tax cuts so big even
OL,4,CLiz Truss might think them gung-ho
OL,6,FIt would scrap VAT on energy bills,
OL,7,Fcut fuel duty, abolish Inheritance Tax
OL,8,Fand reduce Corporation Tax for
OL,9,Fbusinesses.
OL,11,FThe scale of the cuts is huge. Almost
OL,12,F#90 billion a year, according to
OL,13,FReform.
OL,15,FThe plans make the Tories' election
OL,16,Foffering look timid.
