OL,3,CReform promises tax cuts so big even
OL,4,CLiz Truss might think them gung-ho
OL,6,FBy contrast, Labour and the Lib Dems
OL,7,Fplan to increase taxes, although
OL,8,FLabour has ruled out increasing tax in
OL,9,Fany of the big three (income tax,
OL,10,FNational Insurance and VAT).
OL,12,FToo big to be credible? Well, even Liz
OL,13,FTruss might think Reform's tax cuts
OL,14,Fare a little gung-ho.
OL,16,FShe served up #45 billion of cuts in
OL,17,Fher Mini Budget - it was enough to
OL,18,Fspook the markets and bring down her
OL,19,Fgovernment.
