OL,3,CReform promises tax cuts so big even
OL,4,CLiz Truss might think them gung-ho
OL,6,FTruss's problem was she didn't really
OL,7,Fexplain how her tax cuts would be paid
OL,8,Ffor.
OL,10,FReform does. It says it would save
OL,11,F#150 billion by cutting spending
OL,12,Felsewhere - to public services and
OL,13,Fworking-age benefits in particular.
OL,15,FReform says the savings will be closer
OL,16,Fto #160 billion because their policies
OL,17,Fwould raise economic output by 1%,
OL,18,Fgenerating higher tax receipts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
