OL,3,CReform promises tax cuts so big even
OL,4,CLiz Truss might think them gung-ho
OL,6,F"The tax cuts would cost more than
OL,7,Fthey expect. The spending reductions
OL,8,Fwouldn't save as much as they expect
OL,9,Fto the tune of tens of billions of
OL,10,Fpounds a year," says Carl Emerson,
OL,11,Fdeputy director at the IFS.
OL,13,F"In addition, their aspiration to
OL,14,Feliminate waiting lists would be more
OL,15,Fexpensive, even if it can be achieved.
OL,16,FOverall, the package as a whole does
OL,17,Fnot add up."
