OL,4,CLiz Truss might think them gung-ho
OL,6,FThe IFS's analysis puts Reform's
OL,7,Fmanifesto back in Truss territory,
OL,8,Fwhich is not a place any politician
OL,9,Fwould like to be.
OL,11,FThe front page of Reform's manifesto
OL,12,Fshows Nigel Farage in Downing Street.
OL,14,FIf he were to lead the next government
OL,15,F- which he says he won't - the IFS
OL,16,Fbelieves he would find it impossible
OL,17,Fto deliver on all of the promises
OL,18,FReform has made.
